": \"advice\", \"from\": 482, \"to\": 488}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 492, \"to\": 498}, {\"ngram\": \"scams\", \"from\": 514, \"to\": 519}, {\"ngram\": \"falling victim\", \"from\": 530, \"to\": 544}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics begin with the Opening Ceremony on July 26, and are set to last until August 11.\", \"from\": 567, \"to\": 660, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 595, \"end\": 611, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Opening_ceremony\", \"score\": 0.9699641494158031, \"rank\": 0.030629003506015582, \"text\": \"Opening Ceremony\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Opening_ceremony\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Opening_ceremony\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympics\", \"from\": 567, \"to\": 579}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 615, \"to\": 619}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 650, \"to\": 656}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paralympics begin on August 28, and will end on September 8.\", \"from\": 661, \"to\": 725, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Paralympics\", \"from\": 661, \"to\": 676}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 686, \"to\": 692}, {\"ngram\": \"September\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 722}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The anti-fraud division la Brigade de r\\u00e9pression de la d\\u00e9linquance astucieuse (BRDA)said on June 7that scammers have been working on new schemes specifically to coincide with the Olympics, to take advantage of people's enthusiasm and travel plans which are thought to make them more susceptible.\", \"from\": 727, \"to\": 1022, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The anti-fraud division\", \"from\": 727, \"to\": 750}, {\"ngram\": \"la Brigade de r\\u00e9pression de la d\\u00e9linquance astucieuse\", \"from\": 751, \"to\": 804}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 823}, {\"ngram\": \"7that\", \"from\": 824, \"to\": 829}, {\"ngram\": \"scammers\", \"from\": 830, \"to\": 838}, {\"ngram\": \"new schemes\", \"from\": 860, \"to\": 871}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 902, \"to\": 914}, {\"ngram\": \"advantage\", \"from\": 924, \"to\": 933}, {\"ngram\": \"people's enthusiasm and travel plans\", \"from\": 937, \"to\": 973}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ina recent statement, the Assurance maladie said it fears \\\"an upsurge in attempts at fraud and cyber-maliciousness\\\", and especially warned people to be alert to scammers trying to pass themselves off as \\\"agents of your localcaisse d'Assurance maladie\\\".\", \"from\": 1024, \"to\": 1276, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Assurance maladie\", \"from\": 1046, \"to\": 1067}, {\"ngram\": \"an upsurge\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1093}, {\"ngram\": \"attempts\", \"from\": 1097, \"to\": 1105}, {\"ngram\": \"fraud\", \"from\": 1109, \"to\": 1114}, {\"ngram\": \"cyber-maliciousness\", \"from\": 1119, \"to\": 1138}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1163, \"to\": 1169}, {\"ngram\": \"scammers\", \"from\": 1185, \"to\": 1193}, {\"ngram\": \"agents\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1234}, {\"ngram\": \"your localcaisse d'Assurance maladie\", \"from\": 1238, \"to\": 1274}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This \\\"is set to become even more widespread in France during the Olympic and Paralympic Games\\\", it said.\", \"from\": 1278, \"to\": 1382, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1325, \"end\": 1331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999999999863576, \"rank\": 1.2387251201449537e-11, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic and Paralympic Games\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1371}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read also:Watch out for these scams as Paris prepares for 2024 OlympicsRead also:Paris Olympics ticket scams: 338 websites identified for resale fraud The agency has warned people to be especially alert to 'phishing' attempts.\", \"from\": 1384, \"to\": 1611, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1423, \"end\": 1428, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.057245743391768e-20, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1465, \"end\": 1479, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these scams\", \"from\": 1408, \"to\": 1419}, {\"ngram\": \"2024 OlympicsRead\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1459}, {\"ngram\": \"338 websites\", \"from\": 1494, \"to\": 1506}, {\"ngram\": \"resale fraud\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1534}, {\"ngram\": \"The agency\", \"from\": 1535, \"to\": 1545}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1563}, {\"ngram\": \"' attempts\", \"from\": 1599, \"to\": 1609}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is when scammers send emails, texts, or links that appear very similar to real communications from - in this case - the Assurance Maladie.\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1756, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"scammers\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1634}, {\"ngram\": \"emails\", \"from\": 1640, \"to\": 1646}, {\"ngram\": \"texts\", \"from\": 1648, \"to\": 1653}, {\"ngram\": \"links\", \"from\": 1658, \"to\": 1663}, {\"ngram\": \"real communications\", \"from\": 1692, \"to\": 1711}, {\"ngram\": \"this case\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\": 1731}, {\"ngram\": \"the Assurance Maladie\", \"from\": 1734, \"to\": 1755}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The messages usually ask for personal data.\", \"from\": 1757, \"to\": 1800, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The messages\", \"from\": 1757, \"to\": 1769}, {\"ngram\": \"personal data\", \"from\": 1786, \"to\": 1799}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This might include asking for your social security number, your Ameli login details, or bank account details.\", \"from\": 1802, \"to\": 1911, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your social security number\", \"from\": 1832, \"to\": 1859}, {\"ngram\": \"your Ameli login details\", \"from\": 1861, \"to\": 1885}, {\"ngram\": \"bank account details\", \"from\": 1890, \"to\": 1910}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Other common scams include those asking for you to pay to renew your carte Vitale, or to have a new card sent to you.\", \"from\": 1912, \"to\": 2029, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1981, \"end\": 1993, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carte_Vitale\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"carte Vitale\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carte_Vitale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carte_Vitale\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Other common scams\", \"from\": 1912, \"to\": 1930}, {\"ngram\": \"a new card\", \"from\": 2006, \"to\": 2016}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Assurance maladie advises that it will never ask you for: Your bank details Your Ameli details or log in details Your medical details It also states that it will never give you a very tight deadline or pressure you to act within days or hours.\", \"from\": 2031, \"to\": 2282, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Assurance maladie\", \"from\": 2031, \"to\": 2052}, {\"ngram\": \"Your bank\", \"from\": 2093, \"to\": 2102}, {\"ngram\": \"Your Ameli details\", \"from\": 2111, \"to\": 2129}, {\"ngram\": \"details\", \"from\": 2140, \"to\": 2147}, {\"ngram\": \"Your medical details\", \"from\": 2148, \"to\": 2168}, {\"ngram\": \"a very tight deadline\", \"from\": 2212, \"to\": 2233}, {\"ngram\": \"pressure\", \"from\": 2237, \"to\": 2245}, {\"ngram\": \"days\", \"from\": 2264, \"to\": 2268}, {\"ngram\": \"hours\", \"from\": 2272, \"to\": 2277}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Be aware that there is never any cost to have a new carte Vitale made or delivered to you (delivery is always free).\", \"from\": 2284, \"to\": 2400, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2336, \"end\": 2348, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carte_Vitale\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"carte Vitale\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carte_Vitale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carte_Vitale\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any cost\", \"from\": 2313, \"to\": 2321}, {\"ngram\": \"delivery\", \"from\": 2375, \"to\": 2383}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Similarly, a carte Vitale does not need to be 'renewed' regularly.\", \"from\": 2401, \"to\": 2467, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2414, \"end\": 2426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carte_Vitale\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"carte Vitale\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carte_Vitale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carte_Vitale\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It only needs to be updated once a year by your pharmacist.\", \"from\": 2468, \"to\": 2527, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your pharmacist\", \"from\": 2511, \"to\": 2526}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read also:Carte Vitale: What do I do if I lose my French health insurance card?Read also:Carte Vitale scam: People in France warned over fake emails and texts Other common scams include: A request to \\\"update your file\\\" in order to keep receiving reimbursements A request for your bank details (or to confirm them) so they can make a transfer to you An alert about ongoing fraud on your account (Bank or Ameli account).\", \"from\": 2529, \"to\": 2951, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2579, \"end\": 2585, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8763396705421751, \"rank\": 0.14111001711732213, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2618, \"end\": 2630, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carte_Vitale\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carte Vitale\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carte_Vitale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carte_Vitale\"}, {\"begin\": 2647, \"end\": 2653, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999999999863576, \"rank\": 1.2387251201449537e-11, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"People\", \"from\": 2637, \"to\": 2643}, {\"ngram\": \"fake emails\", \"from\": 2666, \"to\": 2677}, {\"ngram\": \"texts Other common scams\", \"from\": 2682, \"to\": 2706}, {\"ngram\": \"A request\", \"from\": 2716, \"to\": 2725}, {\"ngram\": \"your file\", \"from\": 2737, \"to\": 2746}, {\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 2751, \"to\": 2756}, {\"ngram\": \"reimbursements\", \"from\": 2775, \"to\": 2789}, {\"ngram\": \"A request\", \"from\": 2790, \"to\": 2799}, {\"ngram\": \"your bank details\", \"from\": 2804, \"to\": 2821}, {\"ngram\": \"a transfer\", \"from\": 2860, \"to\": 2870}, {\"ngram\": \"An alert\", \"from\": 2878, \"to\": 2886}, {\"ngram\": \"ongoing fraud\", \"from\": 2893, \"to\": 2906}, {\"ngram\": \"your account\", \"from\": 2910, \"to\": 2922}, {\"ngram\": \"Bank or Ameli account\", \"from\": 2924, \"to\": 2945}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A genuine Assurance maladie agent will only contact you using very specific numbers or addresses.\", \"from\": 2953, \"to\": 3050, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A genuine Assurance maladie agent\", \"from\": 2953, \"to\": 2986}, {\"ngram\": \"very specific numbers\", \"from\": 3015, \"to\": 3036}, {\"ngram\": \"addresses\", \"from\": 3040, \"to\": 3049}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Assurance maladie only contacts people from the following numbers: 3646 01 78 85 70 03 SMS messages only come from38 663(and begin with ASSURANCE MALADIE) Clickable links only end with the addressesameli.frorassure.ameli.fr.\", \"from\": 3052, \"to\": 3284, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Assurance maladie\", \"from\": 3052, \"to\": 3073}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3088, \"to\": 3094}, {\"ngram\": \"the following numbers\", \"from\": 3100, \"to\": 3121}, {\"ngram\": \"3646 01 78 85 70 03 SMS messages\", \"from\": 3123, \"to\": 3155}, {\"ngram\": \"ASSURANCE MALADIE\", \"from\": 3192, \"to\": 3209}, {\"ngram\": \"Clickable links\", \"from\": 3211, \"to\": 3226}, {\"ngram\": \"the addressesameli.frorassure.ameli.fr\", \"from\": 3241, \"to\": 3279}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Before clicking on any link (even if it looks like the ones above), hover your mouse over the link, without clicking.\", \"from\": 3286, \"to\": 3403, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any link\", \"from\": 3305, \"to\": 3313}, {\"ngram\": \"the ones\", \"from\": 3337, \"to\": 3345}, {\"ngram\": \"your mouse\", \"from\": 3360, \"to\": 3370}, {\"ngram\": \"the link\", \"from\": 3376, \"to\": 3384}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If the address that comes up on your screen (often in the left-hand corner) appears to redirect you to another site, the link is very probably a scam.\", \"from\": 3404, \"to\": 3554, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the address\", \"from\": 3407, \"to\": 3418}, {\"ngram\": \"your screen\", \"from\": 3436, \"to\": 3447}, {\"ngram\": \"the left-hand corner\", \"from\": 3458, \"to\": 3478}, {\"ngram\": \"another site\", \"from\": 3507, \"to\": 3519}, {\"ngram\": \"the link\", \"from\": 3521, \"to\": 3529}, {\"ngram\": \"a scam\", \"from\": 3547, \"to\": 3553}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Genuine emails from the Assurance maladie will always have one of the following endings: @app.assurance-maladie.fr @assurance-maladie.fr @info.ameli.fr @ameli.fr Any variation on these, even if they are very similar (e.g.\", \"from\": 3556, \"to\": 3782, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Genuine emails\", \"from\": 3556, \"to\": 3570}, {\"ngram\": \"the Assurance maladie\", \"from\": 3576, \"to\": 3597}, {\"ngram\": \"the following endings\", \"from\": 3622, \"to\": 3643}, {\"ngram\": \"@app.assurance-maladie.fr @assurance-maladie.fr @info.ameli.fr\", \"from\": 3645, \"to\": 3707}, {\"ngram\": \"Any variation\", \"from\": 3718, \"to\": 3731}]}, {\"sentence\": \"@ameli-fr.com or @ameli.info.fr), is not genuine.\", \"from\": 3783, \"to\": 3832, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"@ameli-fr.com\", \"from\": 3783, \"to\": 3796}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On calls with genuine Assurance maladie agents, they will always give you their name, department and their CPAM details.\", \"from\": 3834, \"to\": 3954, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"calls\", \"from\": 3837, \"to\": 3842}, {\"ngram\": \"genuine Assurance maladie agents\", \"from\": 3848, \"to\": 3880}, {\"ngram\": \"their name\", \"from\": 3908, \"to\": 3918}, {\"ngram\": \"department\", \"from\": 3920, \"to\": 3930}, {\"ngram\": \"their CPAM details\", \"from\": 3935, \"to\": 3953}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They will also have access to your file.\", \"from\": 3956, \"to\": 3996, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"access\", \"from\": 3976, \"to\": 3982}, {\"ngram\": \"your file\", \"from\": 3986, \"to\": 3995}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They also recommend that when speaking to someone from the Assurance Maladie, you always ask the agent \\\"to tell you the last reimbursement paid into your account (indiquer le dernier remboursement vers\\u00e9 sur votre compte)\\\".\", \"from\": 3998, \"to\": 4220, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 4040, \"to\": 4047}, {\"ngram\": \"the Assurance Maladie\", \"from\": 4053, \"to\": 4074}, {\"ngram\": \"the agent\", \"from\": 4091, \"to\": 4100}, {\"ngram\": \"the last reimbursement\", \"from\": 4114, \"to\": 4136}, {\"ngram\": \"your account\", \"from\": 4147, \"to\": 4159}, {\"ngram\": \"indiquer le dernier remboursement\", \"from\": 4161, \"to\": 4194}, {\"ngram\": \"sur votre compte\", \"from\": 4201, \"to\": 4217}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Check that they are correct before you proceed.\", \"from\": 4222, \"to\": 4269, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Assurance maladie recommends a 6-step process when receiving an SMS or email message: Be alert to emails or messages that you are not expecting Check the address or number of the sender Do not let yourself be taken in by threats or apparent urgency Do not enter any personal details on a non-secure site (sometimes these begin with 'http://' rather than 'https://', or do not show a padlock logo in the browser URL field) Trust your instincts Report any fraudulent SMS or emails You can report a potentially fraudulent email or text message to theofficial Pharos portal, or forward the text message to the same service at 33 700.\", \"from\": 4271, \"to\": 4911, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4339, \"end\": 4342, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SMS\", \"score\": 0.9999999990345714, \"rank\": 9.654159272359266e-10, \"text\": \"SMS\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SMS\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SMS\"}, {\"begin\": 4838, \"end\": 4844, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hvar\", \"score\": 0.8901942937910927, \"rank\": 0.12335026968256319, \"text\": \"Pharos\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hvar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hvar\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Assurance maladie\", \"from\": 4271, \"to\": 4292}, {\"ngram\": \"a 6-step process\", \"from\": 4304, \"to\": 4320}, {\"ngram\": \"emails\", \"from\": 4373, \"to\": 4379}, {\"ngram\": \"messages\", \"from\": 4383, \"to\": 4391}, {\"ngram\": \"the address\", \"from\": 4425, \"to\": 4436}, {\"ngram\": \"number\", \"from\": 4440, \"to\": 4446}, {\"ngram\": \"the sender\", \"from\": 4450, \"to\": 4460}, {\"ngram\": \"threats\", \"from\": 4496, \"to\": 4503}, {\"ngram\": \"apparent urgency\